title: Video: JUDE. – Crystals
content:
Rapidly rising FL duo JUDE.

may only have two tracks to their name so far, but they’ve already become one of the most talked about new ‘blog’ artists of the year. With their Lorde-esque debut Crystals clocking up 60k plays on Soundcloud, followed up by the equally as alluring, Jaded, the two piece have released visuals for the aforementioned Crystals. In keeping with their dark, ever-so mysterious sound, shot entirely in black and white, it’s a worthy further development of ‘JUDE.’.
